WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
<v Michael>Uh-oh, okay, okay, nobody panic.

00:03.000 --> 00:05.000
<v Michael>Listen up, listen up.

00:05.000 --> 00:07.000
<v Michael>Everyone, follow me to the shelter.

00:07.000 --> 00:09.000
<v Michael>We've got enough food for 14 days.

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
<v Michael>After that, we have a difficult conversation.

00:12.000 --> 00:15.000
<v Dwight>My bad. Space heater and fan were both on high,

00:15.000 --> 00:17.000
<v Dwight>plugged into the same outlet, so...

00:17.000 --> 00:20.000
<v Ryan>Uh, it's saying the server went down.

00:20.000 --> 00:22.000
<v Ryan>Does anybody know that password?

00:22.000 --> 00:24.000
<v Ryan>Because otherwise we can't do any work.

00:24.000 --> 00:26.000
<v Michael>Uh-oh, try password.

00:26.000 --> 00:28.000
<v Ryan>Nope.

00:28.000 --> 00:32.000
<v Michael>Try zero, zero, zero. Zero, zero, zero.

00:32.000 --> 00:33.000
<v Ryan>No.

00:33.000 --> 00:37.000
<v Michael>Okay, now try zero, zero, zero. Zero, zero, one.

00:37.000 --> 00:39.000
<v Ryan>Okay, I'm not doing every number.

00:39.000 --> 00:42.000
<v Jim>Wait, um, does anyone remember when it was set up?

00:42.000 --> 00:44.000
<v Dwight>Uh, it was like eight years ago.

00:44.000 --> 00:46.000
<v Kevin>Lord of the Rings stuff?

00:46.000 --> 00:47.000
<v Michael>I don't know.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.000
<v Michael>I'm just trying to think of things that were happening at the time.

00:49.000 --> 00:51.000
<v Michael>Um, everyone was getting their driver's license.

00:51.000 --> 00:54.000
<v Jim>Why don't we just call the IT guy who set it up?

00:54.000 --> 00:56.000
<v Jim>What's the name of the guy in the glasses again?

00:56.000 --> 00:59.000
<v Michael>Okay, moving backwards, our IT guys have been.

00:59.000 --> 01:03.000
<v Michael>Glasses, turban, ear hair, fatty three, shorts, fatty two,

01:03.000 --> 01:05.000
<v Michael>lozenge, and fatso.

01:05.000 --> 01:08.000
<v Dwight>I think lozenge is the one who installed it.

01:08.000 --> 01:10.000
<v Michael>I got it. Try, um...

01:10.000 --> 01:12.000
<v Dwight>Cough, cough, cough, cough.

01:12.000 --> 01:15.000
<v Michael>You know what? It made me laugh when I heard it,

01:15.000 --> 01:17.000
<v Michael>but Pam got really offended.

01:17.000 --> 01:19.000
<v Michael>Big boobs.

01:19.000 --> 01:22.000
<v Oscar>Trauma coin? Nosey?

01:23.000 --> 01:25.000
<v Pam>You're typing big boobs?

01:25.000 --> 01:27.000
<v Michael>I'm trying everything.

01:27.000 --> 01:29.000
<v Dwight>Try big boobs with a Z.

01:29.000 --> 01:31.000
<v Ryan>That's the password. We're in.

01:31.000 --> 01:32.000
<v Jim>All right.

01:32.000 --> 01:33.000
<v Oscar>Wow. Yes.

01:33.000 --> 01:36.000
<v Michael>The important thing is, this kept us secure, people.

